question:
下列配位化合物哪些属于内轨型? 哪些是外轨型?

(1) $\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Cr}}{\left( {\mathrm{H}}_{2}\mathrm{O}\right) }_{6}}\right\rbrack {\mathrm{{Cl}}}_{3}$ ; (2) ${\mathrm{K}}_{3}\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Cr}}{\left( \mathrm{{CN}}\right) }_{6}}\right\rbrack$ ;

(3) ${\mathrm{K}}_{2}\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{PtCl}}}_{4}\right\rbrack$ ; (4) ${\mathrm{K}}_{2}\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Ni}}{\left( \mathrm{{CN}}\right) }_{4}}\right\rbrack$ ;

(5) ${\mathrm{K}}_{4}\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Mn}}{\left( \mathrm{{CN}}\right) }_{6}}\right\rbrack$ ; (6) ${\mathrm{K}}_{3}\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Fe}}{\left( {\mathrm{C}}_{2}{\mathrm{O}}_{4}\right) }_{3}}\right\rbrack$ ;

(7) $\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Fe}}{\left( \mathrm{{CO}}\right) }_{5}}\right\rbrack$ ; (8) ${\mathrm{K}}_{3}\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Fe}}{\left( \mathrm{{CN}}\right) }_{6}}\right\rbrack$ 。

预测下列各对配位单元的相对稳定性, 并简要说明原因。

(1) ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}\right\rbrack }^{3 + }$ 与 ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}\right\rbrack }^{2 + }$ ;

(2) ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Zn}}\left( \mathrm{{EDTA}}\right) \right\rbrack }^{2 - }$ 与 ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Ca}}\left( \mathrm{{EDTA}}\right) \right\rbrack }^{2 - }$ ;

(3) ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Cu}}{\left( \mathrm{{CN}}\right) }_{4}\right\rbrack }^{3 - }$ 与 ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Zn}}{\left( \mathrm{{CN}}\right) }_{4}\right\rbrack }^{2 - }$ ;

(4) ${\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{AlF}}}_{6}\right\rbrack }^{3 - }$ 与 ${\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{AlCl}}}_{6}\right\rbrack }^{3 - }$ ;

(5) ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Cu}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{2}{\mathrm{{CH}}}_{2}\mathrm{{COO}}\right) }_{2}\right\rbrack }_{\text{与 }}{\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Cu}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{2}{\mathrm{{CH}}}_{2}{\mathrm{{CH}}}_{2}{\mathrm{{NH}}}_{2}\right) }_{2}\right\rbrack }^{2 + }$ 。

answer:
(1) 稳定性 ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}\right\rbrack }^{3 + } > {\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}\right\rbrack }^{2 + }$ 因前者中心的正电荷数高、离子半径小, 对配体的引力大;

（2）稳定性 ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Zn}}\left( \mathrm{{EDTA}}\right) \right\rbrack }^{2 - } > {\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Ca}}\left( \mathrm{{EDTA}}\right) \right\rbrack }^{2 - }$ 因 ${\mathrm{{Zn}}}^{2 + }$ 的极化能力和变形性都比 ${\mathrm{{Ca}}}^{2 + }$ 大;

（3）稳定性 ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Cu}}{\left( \mathrm{{CN}}\right) }_{4}\right\rbrack }^{3 - } > {\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Zn}}{\left( \mathrm{{CN}}\right) }_{4}\right\rbrack }^{2 - }\;{\mathrm{{Cu}}}^{ + }$ 是软酸, ${\mathrm{{Zn}}}^{2 + }$ 为交界酸, ${\mathrm{{Cu}}}^{ + }$ 与软碱 ${\mathrm{{CN}}}^{ - }$ 结合更稳定;

（4）稳定性 ${\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{AlF}}}_{6}\right\rbrack }^{3 - } > {\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{AlCl}}}_{6}\right\rbrack }^{3 - }\;{\mathrm{{Al}}}^{3 + }$ 为硬酸,而碱的硬度为 ${\mathrm{F}}^{ - } > {\mathrm{{Cl}}}^{ - }$ ,因而 ${\mathrm{{Al}}}^{3 + }$ 与 ${\mathrm{F}}^{ - }$ 结合更稳定;

(5) 稳定性 ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Cu}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{2}{\mathrm{{CH}}}_{2}{\mathrm{{CH}}}_{2}{\mathrm{{NH}}}_{2}\right) }_{2}\right\rbrack }^{2 + } > \left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Cu}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{2}{\mathrm{{CH}}}_{2}\mathrm{{COO}}\right) }_{2}}\right\rbrack$ 前者配体中配位原子都是 $\mathrm{N}$ ,后者配体中配位原子为 $\mathrm{N}$ 和 $\mathrm{O},\mathrm{N}$ 的配位能力比 $\mathrm{O}$ 强。

在水溶液中, ${E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{Co}}}^{3 + }/{\mathrm{{Co}}}^{2 + }}\right) > {E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{O}}_{2}/{\mathrm{H}}_{2}\mathrm{O}}\right)$ ,因此 ${\mathrm{{Co}}}^{3 + }$ 能氧化水:

$$
4{\mathrm{{Co}}}^{3 + } + 2{\mathrm{H}}_{2}\mathrm{O} = 4{\mathrm{{Co}}}^{2 + } + {\mathrm{O}}_{2} \uparrow + 4{\mathrm{H}}^{ + }
$$

当 ${\mathrm{{Co}}}^{3 + }$ 生成 ${\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}\right\rbrack }^{3 + }$ 后:

$$
{E}^{ \ominus }\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}^{3 + }/\mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}^{2 + }}\right\rbrack = {E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{Co}}}^{3 + }/{\mathrm{{Co}}}^{2 + }}\right) + {0.059}\mathrm{\;V}\lg \frac{c\left( {\mathrm{{Co}}}^{3 + }\right) }{c\left( {\mathrm{{Co}}}^{2 + }\right) }
$$

$$
= {E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{{Co}}}^{3 + }/{\mathrm{{Co}}}^{2 + }}\right) + {0.059}\mathrm{\;V}\lg \frac{{K}_{\text{稳 }}^{ \ominus }\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}^{2 + }}\right\rbrack }{{K}_{\text{稳 }}^{ \ominus }\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}^{3 + }}\right\rbrack }
$$

$$
= {1.92}\mathrm{\;V} + {0.059}\mathrm{\;V}\lg \frac{{1.38} \times {10}^{5}}{{1.58} \times {10}^{35}}
$$

$$
= {0.15}\mathrm{\;V}
$$

在氨溶液中,设 $c\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) = {1.0}\mathrm{\;{mol}} \cdot {\mathrm{{dm}}}^{-3}$ ,则

$$
c\left( {\mathrm{{OH}}}^{ - }\right) = \sqrt{{1.0} \times {1.8} \times {10}^{-5}}\mathrm{\;{mol}} \cdot {\mathrm{{dm}}}^{-3} = {4.24} \times {10}^{-3}\mathrm{\;{mol}} \cdot {\mathrm{{dm}}}^{-3}
$$

$$
{\mathrm{O}}_{2} + 4{\mathrm{H}}_{2}\mathrm{O} + 4{\mathrm{e}}^{ - } = 4{\mathrm{{OH}}}^{ - }
$$

$$
E\left( {{\mathrm{O}}_{2}/{\mathrm{{OH}}}^{ - }}\right) = {E}^{ \ominus }\left( {{\mathrm{O}}_{2}/{\mathrm{{OH}}}^{ - }}\right) + \frac{{0.059}\mathrm{\;V}}{4}\lg \frac{p\left( {\mathrm{O}}_{2}\right) /{p}^{ \ominus }}{{\left\lbrack c\left( {\mathrm{{OH}}}^{ - }\right) \right\rbrack }^{4}}
$$

$$
= {0.401}\mathrm{\;V} + \frac{{0.059}\mathrm{\;V}}{4}\lg \frac{1}{{\left( {4.24} \times {10}^{-3}\right) }^{4}}
$$

$$
= {0.54}\mathrm{\;V}
$$

$$
{E}^{ \ominus }\left\lbrack {\mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}^{3 + }/\mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}^{2 + }}\right\rbrack < E\left( {{\mathrm{O}}_{2}/{\mathrm{{OH}}}^{ - }}\right) \text{,故}{\left\lbrack \mathrm{{Co}}{\left( {\mathrm{{NH}}}_{3}\right) }_{6}\right\rbrack }^{3 + }\text{不能氧化水。}
$$
